Tips:
1. Please named your CLR file name like this "Crl.crl",it will be loaded when verify certificate.
2. Strongly recommended update you library to OpenSSL_1_0_2a or highter version,if you want to verify certificate.
   Or application will crash.

Bugs on verify:
1. Verify false when you click verify button again without change certificate. (Debug done)
2. Application Maybe crash while use CheckCertWithCrl().
3. Display None information while read certificate name.

